title: Tour de France 2008 Stage 1 Highlights
description:
2008 Tour de France - Stage 1 - Monts d&#039;Arree to Cote de Cadoual

The first stage of the Tour de France is a 197.5km ride that begins with the hills of Monts d&#039;Arree and ends at the summit of Cote de Cadoual; the best cyclists from around the world begin their long journey in hopes of the yellow jersey.

Recorded off of Versus network (American TV channel) day of. Includes commercials. Encoded in AVI with DivX and tested working using Quicktime with DivX installed. Running time: 3 hours and 3 minutes.
